{"tid":2304653,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「股神」巴菲特︰蘋果若投資Tesla是差勁主意","createTime":"2020-11-29T04:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T06:06:10.000Z","uid":181502,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"0483b5ba05529b872c0274607609c61e7a375460","tid":2304653,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">18:53 2018/08/31</span></span><br />\n主意<br />\n 國際形勢 18:53 2018/08/31  <br />\n「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）堪稱是蘋果的忠實支持者，但認為蘋果假若投資電動車廠特斯拉（Tesla）會是「非常差勁的主意」（very poor idea），認為汽車業經營不易。不過，巴菲特強調，無論如何支持蘋果行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook）。<br />\n<br />\n 巴菲特（Warren Buffett）<br />\n▲ 巴菲特（Warren Buffett）<br />\n<br />\n對於坊間有分析師和投資者認為蘋果會投資Tesla，巴菲特卻不認同，認為汽車業競爭大，經營難，有資金有實力的大車廠比比皆是。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他形容Tesla經營與眾不同且處境艱難，汽車行業先行者並無優勢，即使今年暫時領先對手，對手可以抄襲（copy），來年隨時被後來居上，形容投資Tesla是「非常差勁的主意」（very poor idea）。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，財力雄厚的蘋果近年致力投資研發自動駕駛汽車，2014年開展的「泰坦計劃」（Project Titan），部門人數不斷增加，至今已聘用逾千工程師，當中不少是從Tesla高薪挖角而來。<br />\n<br />\n風險投資公司Loup Ventures創辦人之一蒙斯特（Gene Munster）大膽預測，Tesla的電動車業務若明年仍未有利潤，一哥地位遲早不保，遭蘋果大舉收購並非無可能。但他亦補充，要買斷Tesla股份，須得大多數Tesla股東支持，並非易事。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特強調仍然支持蘋果，透露近期增持了「少許」蘋果股份，據巴郡（Berkshire Hathaway）向監管機構的申報文件，巴郡於今年次季增持1240萬股蘋果股份，截至6月30日，總持股量增至2.52億股或5.2%。<br />\n<br />\n被問及Tesla創辦人馬斯（Elon Musk）在Twitter披露私有化的事件，巴菲特形容這只是失言，任何人都可能犯錯，問題在於「失言後應馬上更正」。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特續稱，若易地而處，公司股份在他發表「取得資金」言論後數分鐘，即出現瘋狂交投，他肯定會馬上補充「我認為我能取得資金，或其他類似言論」。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯言論引發連串風波，遭質疑操控股價，美國證券交易委員會（SEC）介入調查，在巨大輿論壓力下馬斯早前宣布放棄私有化。"},{"pid":"6d9b82849c65d65d50f8b920b1f4b73568db436e","tid":2304653,"uid":101328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"巴佬D金放曬未？"},{"pid":"5da60cc17b041c9d945bfaf00dbb4eb49e6354b0","tid":2304653,"uid":186543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"比亞迪支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be192a3e274c2b1eabdae5059094713e7ad4c29","tid":2304653,"uid":180251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"咁有錢私有化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d184dac7e72608c94171cebaf939de1e6cc49093","tid":2304653,"uid":54337,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"連登仔：巴菲特係廢老"},{"pid":"42719dd5b69491c7f69a6cd402cc1d0398293551","tid":2304653,"uid":957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8be192a3e274c2b1eabdae5059094713e7ad4c29","tid":2304653,"uid":180251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"咁有錢私有化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"18 年420蚊果陣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f16479643a2646793e73e0c008279116d1881ee","tid":2304653,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42719dd5b69491c7f69a6cd402cc1d0398293551","tid":2304653,"uid":957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8be192a3e274c2b1eabdae5059094713e7ad4c29","tid":2304653,"uid":180251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"咁有錢私有化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"18 年420蚊果陣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"係依家的$70-80之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b709b62035317dcc1b00d4f3aae1aa7f9b4f20b","tid":2304653,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"廢老<img s